Titolo: Clue (1998 video game)

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Clue (known as Cluedo outside of North America) is a 1998 video game based on the board game of the same name. It is also known as Clue: Murder at Boddy Mansion or Cluedo: Murder at Blackwell Grange, depending on whether the country of release used American or British English.Clue runs on Microsoft Windows. It was developed in 1998 for Hasbro Interactive by EAI.  Infogrames (now Atari) took over publishing rights for the game in 2000 when Hasbro Interactive went out of business. The game, just like the board game, is meant for 3-6 players due to the six suspects. The game garnered generally positive reviews upon release. 
Engineering Animation released a spin-off named Clue Chronicles: Fatal Illusion in 1999.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
